-    if (heart_rate_valid) {
+
+    // Heart rate: autocorrelation estimator with signal-quality gating.
+    // Effective sample rate = sampleRate 100 Hz / sampleAverage 4 = 25 Hz.
+    // Readings with a low SQI (motion, poor contact, no wearer) are suppressed
+    // instead of being sent over the mesh as confident-looking wrong values.
